name: AI Chat - Google Gemini
description: Executes a one-off prompt to Google Gemini and returns the generated text result
introductoryText:
![Gemini](data:image/png;base64,)
### AI Chat with Google Gemini
#### Executes a one-off prompt request for each row in the input block, and output the results from Gemini using the specified text generation / chat completion model
